## benchResult variable

Similar to [bench](./bench.bench.md)<!-- -->, but produces no output and instead returns tuple of `fn`<!-- -->'s last result and the grand total time measurement.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
benchResult: <T>(fn: () => T, n?: number) => TimingResult<T>
```
